---
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'Cigna Global in Ecuador', level: 2 },
  { id: 'why-cigna', text: 'Why Cigna for Ecuador', level: 2 },
  { id: 'plans-and-pricing', text: 'Plans and Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'coverage-details', text: 'Coverage Details', level: 2 },
  { id: 'retiree-considerations', text: 'Retiree Considerations', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Health Insurance in Ecuador', href: '/countries/ecuador/insurance' },
  { title: 'Cigna Global Review', href: '/providers/cigna-global' },
  { title: 'Cigna vs BUPA', href: '/compare/cigna-global-vs-bupa-global' },
];

const planColumns = [
  { key: 'plan', header: 'Plan' },
  { key: 'coverage', header: 'Coverage' },
  { key: 'price', header: 'Price (Age 55)' },
];

const planRows = [
  { plan: 'Silver', coverage: 'Core inpatient', price: '$240-300/mo' },
  { plan: 'Gold', coverage: 'Inpatient + outpatient', price: '$300-380/mo' },
  { plan: 'Platinum', coverage: 'Comprehensive', price: '$380-450/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="Cigna Global Health Insurance in Ecuador"
  description="Guide to Cigna Global international health insurance for expats and retirees in Ecuador. Comprehensive coverage with US evacuation options."
  headline="Cigna Global in Ecuador"
  subheadline="Premium international coverage for Ecuador's retiree community. Strong support and medical evacuation to the US when needed."
  heroBackgroundImage="/images/countries/ecuador-hero-bg.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get a Cigna Quote"
  ctaButtonHref="/go/cigna-global"
>
  <h2 id="overview">Cigna Global in Ecuador</h2>
  <p>
    Cigna Global is a top choice for retirees in Ecuador who want comprehensive coverage and the option to access US healthcare for complex conditions. With strong care coordination and medical evacuation benefits, Cigna provides peace of mind.
  </p>
  <p>
    For those who may need specialized care beyond what Ecuador offers, Cigna's global network and US coverage options are particularly valuable.
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">$300-450</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Monthly (Age 55)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">US Coverage</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">Available option</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-600">Evacuation</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">To appropriate facility</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Get Your Cigna Ecuador Quote"
    description="Comprehensive coverage for Ecuador retirees."
    buttonText="Get Quote"
    buttonHref="/go/cigna-global"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="why-cigna">Why Cigna for Ecuador</h2>

  <h3>Medical Evacuation</h3>
  <p>
    While Ecuador handles most medical needs, complex cases may require evacuation. Cigna provides:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Evacuation to nearest appropriate facility</li>
    <li>Option for US evacuation for complex care</li>
    <li>Coordination with US specialists if needed</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>US Coverage Options</h3>
  <p>
    For retirees who visit the US or prefer US care for certain conditions:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Plans available with US coverage included</li>
    <li>Access to US hospital networks</li>
    <li>Seamless coverage when visiting family</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Retiree-Friendly Features</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Lifetime renewability guarantee</li>
    <li>No upper age limit with underwriting</li>
    <li>Pre-existing condition options</li>
    <li>Wellness programs</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="plans-and-pricing">Plans and Pricing</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={planColumns} rows={planRows} />
  </div>

  <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 italic">
    Prices shown for healthy 55-year-old. Premiums increase significantly with age.
  </p>

  <h3>Cost Factors</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Age:</strong> Significant increases after 60 and 65</li>
    <li><strong>US coverage:</strong> Adding US increases premiums 30-50%</li>
    <li><strong>Deductible:</strong> Higher deductibles reduce costs 20-30%</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="coverage-details">Coverage Details</h2>

  <h3>What's Covered</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Inpatient:</strong> Hospital stays, surgery, ICU</li>
    <li><strong>Outpatient:</strong> Doctor visits, specialists (Gold+)</li>
    <li><strong>Emergency:</strong> Worldwide emergency coverage</li>
    <li><strong>Evacuation:</strong> To appropriate facility including US</li>
    <li><strong>Cancer:</strong> Full treatment coverage</li>
    <li><strong>Chronic conditions:</strong> Covered after waiting period</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Limitations</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Pre-existing conditions: 2-year moratorium or underwriting</li>
    <li>Mental health: Limited, varies by plan</li>
    <li>Dental/vision: Optional add-on</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="retiree-considerations">Retiree Considerations</h2>

  <h3>Age-Related Pricing</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Age 55:</strong> $300-450/month</li>
    <li><strong>Age 65:</strong> $450-650/month</li>
    <li><strong>Age 75:</strong> $600-900/month</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Pre-existing Conditions</h3>
  <p>
    Cigna offers moratorium (2-year exclusion) or full underwriting options for pre-existing conditions—important for retirees who often have health histories.
  </p>

  <h3>Combining with IESS</h3>
  <p>
    Many retirees use both Cigna and IESS: Cigna for comprehensive coverage and evacuation, IESS (~$80-100/month) for routine local care.
  </p>

  <CTABox
    title="Compare Cigna Plans for Ecuador"
    description="Find the right coverage for your needs."
    buttonText="Get Quote"
    buttonHref="/go/cigna-global"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Prices and coverage are estimates. Get a personalized quote for accurate pricing.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
